    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. The exterior shows some clear signs of age, including a few noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all major electronics are still functional. Mechanically, it runs well, but it will likely need some routine maintenance soon, such as new brake pads and a suspension tune-up. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation at a reasonable price.",
