      "description": "Get ready for a rewarding project! This car is a fantastic opportunity for anyone looking for a budget-friendly vehicle they can work on themselves. It's in poor condition and will require some dedicated mechanical and cosmetic TLC to get back on the road, making it the perfect choice for a mechanic's special or a restoration project!",
