      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and meticulous upkeep. The exterior maintains a brilliant luster, having been consistently garaged and hand-washed. While you may find a few minor stone chips on the lower front bumper consistent with careful highway driving, the body panels are remarkably straight and free of any significant blemishes. Step inside to a cabin that still feels fresh and inviting. The leather upholstery has been regularly conditioned; it shows light, natural softening on the driver\u2019s bolster but remains free of cracks or stains. All interior technology, including the dual-zone climate control and the premium infotainment suite, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the car is in excellent health. It comes with a full service portfolio documenting on-time oil changes and preventative maintenance. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts with precision, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. With a recent multi-point inspection and plenty of life left on the tires, this car is ready to provide its next owner with years of reliable service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
